
📦 package.json — Declares Dependencies & Scripts

`json
{
  "name": "hudverse-site",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "private": true,
  "scripts": {
    "dev": "next dev",
    "build": "next build",
    "start": "next start"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "@supabase/supabase-js": "^2.0.0",
    "next": "13.5.2",
    "react": "18.2.0",
    "react-dom": "18.2.0"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "tailwindcss": "^3.3.2",
    "postcss": "^8.4.24",
    "autoprefixer": "^10.4.14"
  }
}
`

---

⚙️ next.config.js — Next.js Configuration

`js
/ @type {import('next').NextConfig} */
const nextConfig = {
  reactStrictMode: true,
  images: {
    domains: ['your-image-domains.com'], // optional if using external images
  },
};

module.exports = nextConfig;
`

---

🎨 tailwind.config.js — Tailwind Setup

`js
/ @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */
module.exports = {
  content: [
    './src/pages//*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx}',
    './src/components//*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx}'
  ],
  theme: {
    extend: {
      colors: {
        mythpunk: '#7e22ce',
        solarpunk: '#22c55e',
        cyberpunk: '#0ea5e9'
      },
      animation: {
        glow: 'pulse 2s infinite'
      }
    }
  },
  plugins: []
}
`

---

🧪 postcss.config.js — Required for Tailwind

`js
module.exports = {
  plugins: {
    tailwindcss: {},
    autoprefixer: {},
  },
}
`
